Pen: 40

Used by: Knights of Solamnia

This is pretty much a carbon copy of the draconian claymore, however is wielded
by knight npcs.


deadly footman's lance (/d/Krynn/solamn/vin/weapon/kn_lance)

Creator: Arman

Hit: 43
Pen: 45

Used by: Knights of Solamnia

This lance has some minor enchantments put on it, increasing its hit and pen slightly.



tempered spear (/d/Ansalon/goodlund/nethosak/forest/obj/weapon/spear)

Creator: Elmore, April 2001

Modified by: Navarre, October 2005

Hit: 32+random(5)
Pen: 48+random(2)
Speed: 32+random(10)

Wielding: left hand

Guarded by: Ancient Black Dragon (Onyx) on Mithas

(Original spear: two-handed, hit: 40, pen: 40.)


This spear can be found in the corpse of a kender laying in the caves of the 
ancient black dragon, Onyx, in the swamp area of the forest on Mithas.

To obtain the spear the player must first defeat the tough dragon, and figure
out, and be strong enough to pull the roots to reveal the crack to enter.
It is limited who can enter the crack after the dragon has been defeated, 
depending on the constitution of the player. Players of significant 
constitution will not be able to enter the crack.



stone giant thighbone (/d/Krynn/tharkadan/weapon/giant_thighbone.c)

    Creator : Arman

    A two-handed magical club, the thighbone cut from the corpse of
