    Creator : Arman

    A massive two-handed battleaxe made of the rare star metal ore.
    Found on the battlefields of the Dwarfgate Wars, is a chance of
    being wielded by ogre barbarians of the Tharkadan ranges
    (~tharkadan/living/ogre.c). 25% chance of an ogre wielding an 
    axe, with a clone_unique set at 15.

    High hit and pen. Lower chance of dulling/corroding/breaking.
    Very heavy.

    hit: 45; pen: 55

