narwhal hornblade (/d/Krynn/turbidus_ocean/obj/hornblade.c)

    Creator : Arman

    This knife has high hit/pen, however its main power is that a
    waterbreathing effect can be activated upon the wielder if their
    spellcraft is superior amateur or higher. 
    This effect costs 100 mana (base propchange spell x5) upon activation,
    and lasts for 30 minutes or until the blade is unwielded.

    /d/Krynn/turbidus_ocean/spells/waterbreathe.c
    /d/Krynn/turbidus_ocean/spells/waterbreathe_sh.c

    It can be wielded by sahuagin priestesses (clone unique 15)
    /d/Krynn/turbidus_ocean/living/sahuagin_priestess.c

