  Creators: Teth and Aridor

      A magical neck armour that has a few minor magics. It is the
      talisman of Clerics of Morgion. If a Knight of Solamnia attempts
      to wear it, they lose some prestige. This is repeatable and
      additive effect. If someone of align > 400 and has their
      current stat > or = their base stat in both con and dex,
      then the amulet will add_tmp_stat for both dex and con,
      halving the stats. In addition, this amulet also has the effect
      of being able to count how many livings in the room have
      Krynn's 'sickness' poison (see the doc on POISONS).

    Worn by: Cleric of Morgion (/d/Krynn/common/npcs/wand_cl_morgion.c)

             Found randomly over the entire domain.



